And maybe when we come back in September after a conference, we connect and we invite the person that runs the CCSR, is that right?

856
01:21:15,444 --> 01:21:28,536
And we can invite them as a guest to this, and we can say, listen, we're interested in having some students who would like to engage with our commission as part of civic responsibility.

857
01:21:29,216 --> 01:21:29,416
No.

858
01:21:30,177 --> 01:21:31,638
We can try.

859
01:21:32,378 --> 01:21:34,660
Sue, you look hopeful.

860
01:21:34,840 --> 01:21:35,661
I know, Sue.

861
01:21:35,901 --> 01:21:36,962
Yeah, I've tried, yeah.

862
01:21:37,702 --> 01:21:46,188
I'm not going to add much, but is there a way to reach out to organizations that work with young people or parents or something?

863
01:21:46,548 --> 01:21:51,712
Because over here in Medford, do kids go to charter schools where they don't go to Medford High School?

864
01:21:53,537 --> 01:21:58,903
I don't know to be quite honest with you, but but I do know that it does not come through me.

865
01:21:59,464 --> 01:22:10,336
Everybody who is in anybody who's interested in being on a commission has to go to through the city website there's the set process that is used, and it is correct and it's that way.

866
01:22:11,716 --> 01:22:13,198
for many people.

867
01:22:14,319 --> 01:22:27,596
I have dropped hints in my conversation with organizations that support people with disabilities that are housed in Medford, you know, but that is about as far as we can go.

868
01:22:28,677 --> 01:22:36,280
Oh, okay, I just said that only because you mentioned inviting the person from the Medford High School.

869
01:22:36,820 --> 01:22:42,443
Well, the CCSR is the Center for Citizen Responsibility, is that what it's called?

870
01:22:42,963 --> 01:22:46,104
Oh, that's not the person, that's not the Medford High School program?

871
01:22:46,724 --> 01:22:48,265
Okay, okay.

872
01:22:48,345 --> 01:22:50,526
I think it's through Medford High School.

873
01:22:50,546 --> 01:22:52,527
Yeah, it's through Medford High.

874
01:22:53,087 --> 01:22:55,088
Right, that's the kind of stuff that they do.

875
01:22:58,327 --> 01:22:59,288
All right.

876
01:22:59,688 --> 01:23:01,089
Corresponding some announcements.

877
01:23:05,833 --> 01:23:06,854
